PrecisAmendments to the COSMETIC REGULATIONS (SCHEDULE NO. 878) which will require that cosmetic products containing chemicals that may be toxic when ingested be packaged in child-resistant containers and be labelled with hazard symbols, warnings and first-aid statements.
